Imagen is a Python module to handle image metadata.

Actually that's a lie, all it can do right now is chunk PNGs.

Installing
----------
 $ ./setup.py build
 $ su -c "./setup.py install"

Documentation
-------------
The primary documentation for Imagen is the doc strings found in
the source code.
 $ pydoc imagen
 $ pydoc imagen.<module>

The tools/ directory contains several useful examples.

The API-NOTES file lists parts of the API that are either unstable or 
will be removed in the future.

Testing the Module
------------------
To run our test suite,
 $ ./setup.py test
